title: Inkwell Saturday Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, British
description: Food is served by a team of volunteers. Offers a variety of sandwiches plus kids meals, starters, salads, a burger, plus baked goods. Drinks include organic fair trade coffee, tea, herbal teas, and soft drinks. Uses vegetables and herbs from its own garden. Supports Leeds Minds which provides services for people with mental illness. Funky interior with local artwork on walls.
